channel.title: I have a problem
channel.description:
Hey you guys what is up? Ok so I have a "Max cash shop" that sells certificates for 1 coin. I want to make it cost 2147M. How can i do this? Please help. This link goes to my YouTube video about it. http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wNVpbJPwFc4

item.title: I have a problem
item.dc:creator: @GodexCAB GodexCAB
item.description:
@GodexCAB wrote:

[quote=“Teem_Rocket, post:2, topic:516567”]You probably have a file labeled “Item.cfg”. Open that and go down to the I.D. of your item. You might see something like:

20000000	20000000	20000000	0	0	0	0	0	53	55	73	2	52	0	3

The first three values are what you want to edit (I’m not sure about the order, but I believe they’re low alch/high alch/sell price).[/quote]

Thank you.
